  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to determine the frequency and to identify main risk factors
      for venous thromboembolism of venous thromboembolic complications in a population of cancer
      patients treated with a curative intent by ionizing radiation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
